  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate 100 Special Needs Children in Kibera Slum</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">According to a survey done by the United Nations Development Program, 2% of the estimated  2 million children with disabilities in Kenya have access to some form of education. Majority of the disabled children with no access to education live in the urban slums. Littlerock is the only Early Childhood Education Centre in Kibera informal settlement that caters to special needs children. The Centre plans to focus on the education foundation of 100 disabled children in an inclusive setting.</narrative>
  </description>
